Text: Nice movie and nice quality but whas is in that briefcase? Many thanks for the share!!
Steve Austin movie hu? it is probably a real stinker but I am gonna give it a shot......

It's so horribly bad the actors and anyone who was even remotely involved in the making of the movie should be crucified (tied, not nailed).
The first 5 minutes of the movie set the tone of what will be 90 minutes of utter complete horribleness. SWAT-guys carrying around memento-BB guns, taking on bad guys with beef jerky instead of the guns theyre carrying, horrible puns...... UUUUUUUUGH
This movie is only believable because cops are really that stupid!!

and I was right, this movie is a piece of crap.....you figure at least the ex WWE dudes would be able to act, I mean they had plenty of training while in the WWE, but nope, who ever produced this piece of crap should be shot on sight......what a waste of time....but then again I had nothing else to watch so I guess it served it's purpose, kill time.......never again I will delete this crap right now before it fs up my PC.......
Its honestly kind of unbelievable that this movie is as bad as it actually is. Its like it was made by a group of 15-year olds as a school project.
